{"tid":1515557,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［前建制核心］袁彌昌教左我地兩招大絕","createTime":"2019-08-29T08:10:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T19:12:08.000Z","uid":238101,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"daa267495686457b9d8cd7803be36044cc974f6c","tid":1515557,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:10:09.000Z","msg":"又係容海恩老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />節錄專訪比大家睇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[size=6］1. 區選必須重創建制派，才可有機左右特首選舉大局[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n袁彌昌披露，建制派7月的內部民調顯示，<span style=\"color: red;\">建制派支持度由此前的接近五成，下滑至三成，甚至更低[/red］，「（這個下滑）是很恐怖的，對任何政黨和政團來說都是毀滅性的打擊。」<br />\n<br />\n在2015年的區議會選舉，建制陣營囊括431個議席中的299席，佔比近七成，但今年11月的區議會選舉，建制派則人人自危。袁彌昌強調，區議會若然脫離建制派的控制，將對建制派造成致命打擊。[red]目前，1200名的行政長官選委當中，有近一成、即117席由當選的區議員互選，區議會的組成有機會左右特首人選的大局。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.  要外國勢力加持，攬炒路線必須要炒得更要，最好真。攬炒</span><br />\n<br />\n本身為國際政治研究者，袁彌昌從更大的國際局勢分析，他認為反修例運動若沒有新冷戰的大環境，根本就不會去到這個層次。袁彌昌表示，逃犯條例修訂引來「外國勢力」的介入很合理，因為本來的修訂令外國人最受影響，加上孟晚舟事件令大家有戒心，擔心「中國找一些人拘捕、祭旗。」 <br />\n<br />\n「你（外國人）可能去中國的機會比較少，但來香港的機會會比較大，（擔心）隨時都抓幾個。」<br />\n<br />\n「舊時人們可能會覺得，香港回歸你想怎樣就怎樣，但<span style=\"color: red;\">現在中國越來越強勢，人們發展出的敘事是今日香港，明日世界，令人看到原來（中國）這一制這麼可怕，令到中國失掉好多分。</span>這個就見到是新冷戰的序幕，是價值式、意識形態式的，在香港先交鋒一次。」<br />\n<br />\n原文：《專訪新民黨前政策總裁袁彌昌：建制派將面對「毀滅式打擊」》 <a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20190829-hongkong-interview-derekyuen/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20190829-hongkong-interview-derekyuen%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=02d58ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20190829-hongkong-interview-derekyuen/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy;️ 端傳媒 Initium Media"},{"pid":"dd6dd05770fd2e05defd113bf99d4098eee05876","tid":1515557,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d080faa3cc64a98259de4d136b5e2fbfe365b01c","tid":1515557,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:11:10.000Z","msg":"11月區選不可失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現階段必需真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644f89b87745f547eda6a983db4c35c43ce32600","tid":1515557,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ifcqnMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FifcqnMz.png&h=19bda72c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taez0yf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftaez0yf.png&h=868ecca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTpDjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTpDjV.png&h=ada7f3ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4600129d71d3a08b94909db5da401b6ba7b8314","tid":1515557,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食屎啦共狗都唔要嘅教棍學畜偽君子，返去驗下個B嘅DNA再屌爆多幾次隻支那共享雞仲好啦！！！</span></span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dee9cd45cddf727bd13ff6af8e409522efa11d","tid":1515557,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:02:10.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb558623298a00093ba4f667af638749ef569ee","tid":1515557,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0